com.amazonaws.services.elasticsearch

Class AbstractAWSElasticsearchAsync

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amazonaws.services.elasticsearch.AbstractAWSElasticsearch
      • com.amazonaws.services.elasticsearch.AbstractAWSElasticsearchAsync
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AWSElasticsearch, AWSElasticsearchAsync

    public class AbstractAWSElasticsearchAsync
extends AbstractAWSElasticsearch
implements AWSElasticsearchAsync
    Abstract implementation of AWSElasticsearchAsync. Convenient method forms pass through to the corresponding overload that takes a request object and an AsyncHandler, which throws an UnsupportedOperationException.
